data.description: This impeccably maintained, move-in-ready home with a BRAND NEW ROOF is situated in the highly regarded Northgate High School District, alongside the newly established Blake Bass Middle School. As you approach, you'll be greeted by the inviting Southern charm of the substantial rocking chair front porch. Upon entering, you'll immediately notice freshly painted walls and trim, BRAND NEW light fixtures throughout, a coffered ceiling gracing the dining room, a flex room off the two story foyer that can be a formal living or office. hardwood flowing throughout main. and a formal living room that opens up to a recently enclosed porch complete with a fireplace. The kitchen features granite countertops that transform it into a culinary haven. Venturing downstairs, you'll find a fully finished basement that offers limitless possibilities, whether you envision it as a game room, home theater, or a cozy retreat as well as a great storage space for a workshop and a full bathroom! Don't miss the BRAND NEW LVP for comfort and durability! Every bathroom boasts all-new vanities, showcasing a commitment to both quality and style. The master bedroom suite has undergone a complete renovation, featuring a soaking tub, frameless shower, and a generously-sized walk-in closet that will surely delight any fashion enthusiast. Don't miss the BRAND NEW carpet upstairs!! The true showstopper is the "To Die For" screened porch, complete with its own outdoor fireplace. There's even a rescreening in progress, ensuring you can enjoy this exceptional space year-round. This home is conveniently located to I-85 for quick travels to Atlanta and the airport. Don't let this opportunity pass you by. Schedule a viewing today and experience the epitome of suburban living in this sweet, quiet neighborhood!
